		<h3>Flatpak</h3>
		<p>A flatpak contains all the needed dependencies (except the original game assets) and runs in a sandboxed environment.</p>
		<p><a href="https://flathub.org/apps/details/com.corsixth.corsixth" class="action">Download from Flathub</a></p>

		<h3>Package manager</h3>
		<p>Debian/Ubuntu:</p>
		<pre><code>sudo apt install corsix-th</code></pre>
		<p>Fedora:</p>
		<pre><code>sudo dnf install corsix-th</code></pre>
		<p>For other distributions, <a href="https://repology.org/project/corsixth/versions">check on Repology</a> if a package is available.</p>
